<div style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2023/04/pexels-andrea-piacquadio-3771835.jpg" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" border="0" data-original-height="4787" data-original-width="7182" height="426" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2023/04/pexels-andrea-piacquadio-3771835-300x200.jpg" width="640" /></a></div>
