<p><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; font-size: 16px;">Greece is a romantic destination that attracts couples from all over the world. To make the most of your romantic getaway in Greece, consider staying in one of the many intimate villas that the country has to offer. These villas offer privacy, luxury, and breathtaking views of the Aegean Sea. Here are some of the best romantic villas in Greece.</span></p>
